title: 1 Bed Unit Amenity Rich Building in Logan Square - Parking available
posting_body: ['PROPERTY INFO', 'ID: 302356615', 'Rent: $2,840 / Month', 'Beds: 1', 'Bath: 1', 'Available Date: 08/01/2022', 'Pet: Pet Friendly', 'Parking:: attached garage', 'Looking for a subletter for this beautiful 1 bed 1 bath apartment at the Logan Apartments building!', 'Available as soon as Mid-July through 3/20/23 with the option to re-sign.', 'This unit is one of the only 1 bedroom units in the building with a private balcony facing Milwaukee ave.', 'The apartment is available furnished for an additional $500/mo with the opportunity to own most of the furniture after the lease is up.', 'AMENITIES:', 'Co-Working Lounge', 'Fitness Center', 'Demonstration Kitchen', 'Resident Lounge', 'Conference Room', 'Pool and Sun Terrace', 'Cabanas and Firepit', 'Grilling Stations', 'Dog Run', 'Complimentary Bike Storage', '2nd Floor Covered Parking Garage', 'FEATURES:', 'White Quartz Countertops', 'Porcelain Tile Backsplash', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Vinyl Plank Flooring', 'Sound-Insulated Windows', 'Roller Shades', "9' Foot Ceilings", 'In-Unit Washer-Dryer', 'Custom Walk-in Closets', 'Smart Door & Building Locks', 'CONVENIENCES:', 'Package Delivery', 'Lobby Concierge', 'Secure Lobby Entry', 'Onsite Management', 'Livly Concierge App', 'Indoor Entrance to Target', 'Monthly service bundle is $95 for water, trash, recycling and gas, Tenants are responsible for all other utilities.', 'Garage Parking available for $225/mo.', 'PLEASE NOTE: All applicants must have a credit score of 650+ and make a combined income of 3x the monthly rent.', 'FEATURES', 'Business Center', 'Buzzer System / Secured Entry', 'Central Air', 'Concierge', 'Courtyard', 'Deck/Patio', 'Dishwasher', 'Eat-In Kitchen', 'Elevator', 'Fitness Center', 'Gym In-Building', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Laundry in Unit', 'Microwave', 'Oven/Range', 'Pool', 'Private Porch/Balcony', 'Refrigerator', 'Renovated Bathroom', 'Renovated Kitchen', 'Renovated Kitchens', 'Roof Deck', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Sun Deck']
